    "text": "(a) for the words, \u201cLicensing of Shipping Agents, Freight Forwarders, Non - Vessel Operating Common Carriers and Container Operators Act\u201d, of the words \u201cLicensing of Shipping Agents, Freight Forwarders and Non-Vessel Operating Common Carriers Act\u201d; and",
